* Fri Dec 07 2018 Chris Tessmer <chris.tessmer@onyxpoint.com> - 0.3.0-0

- Added
  - Support for SIMP 6.3.0
  - New helper modules under `spec/acceptance/support/lib/`:
    - Simp::IntegrationTest::Helpers
      - Available to all suites (via `spec_helper_acceptance.rb`)
    - Simp::IntegrationTest::ErrataHelpers
      - Provides `simp_errata()` method to check for errata conditions and
        apply fixes for them
    - Simp::IntegrationTest::UpgradeHelpers
  - In `default` suite:
    - New test `puppet agent runs work`
- Changed
  - In `default` suite:
    - "integration_tests class" test renamed to "puppet apply smoke test"


* Fri Sep 28 2018 Chris Tessmer <chris.tessmer@onyxpoint.com> - 0.2.0-0

- Added
  - `upgrade` suite
    - Working 6.1.0 -> 6.2.0 upgrade tests
    - ISO upload support
    - RPM injection support (rough)
- Changed
  - Improved README
  - Tidied up nodeset
- Removed
  - beakerdsl files
  - Module files (part two)

* Thu Sep 13 2018 Chris Tessmer <chris.tessmer@onyxpoint.com> - 0.1.0

